	<img style="width: 100%" src='/img/susana.jpg' align="bottom"/>
      </div>
      
    <ul class="col offset-l1 l6 m6 s12">
      <li>The Santa Susana Field Laboratory (SSFL) is located 30 miles northwest of downtown Los Angeles in southeastern Ventura County. A former rocket engine test and nuclear research facility, the 2,849-acre field laboratory is currently the focus of a comprehensive environmental investigation and cleanup program. The cleanup program addresses contamination in soil, groundwater and, furthering progress toward restoration and preservation of ecosystem. </li>
    </ul>
    </div>


